<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-ebea0b6c8c201c98f3fd3e6685ce2eebcaa54f45">The Quarterstaff 'Eriril' (1d9) (+3,+5)</h2>
<em>The radiant golden staff of an Istari of legend, this wizard's companion grants keen sight and the knowledge of many hidden things.</em> <p>
It can be activated for identify spell every 10 turns if it is being worn. It can be used to store a spell. It increases your intelligence and wisdom by 4. It fights against evil with holy fury. It provides resistance to light. It allows you to see invisible monsters. It allows you to sense the presence of evil beings. 
</p>
